1
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:55,740
=Sugar and Lies=
(A Different Her: The Women's Trilogy)

2
00:00:56,820 --> 00:00:59,780
=Episode 11=
=Sad People Shouldn't Listen to Sad Songs=

3
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,200
Ding Daang.

4
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,280
Ding Daang.

5
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,680
Ding Daang, what are you doing?

6
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,920
Are you out of your mind?

7
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:56,840
All this for some guy?

8
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,800
Is he really worth it?

9
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:01,120
You were exactly like this
when he left back then.

10
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,240
It's been so many years.

11
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:06,600
Why can't you just let yourself move on?

12
00:02:11,320 --> 00:02:12,960
Tell me, am I just useless?

13
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,480
I can't keep the one I love

14
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,880
or see who truly cares about me.

15
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,640
Ding Daang.

16
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,000
Don't talk about yourself like that.

17
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,520
They just weren't good enough for you.

18
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,720
But why?

19
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:40,320
Why is it so hard to forget someone?

20
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,640
Sometimes I really just want to

21
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,200
rip your heart out.

22
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,440
Would taking my heart out

23
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,960
make it hurt less?

24
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,600
Silly one.

25
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,640
It's okay.

26
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:03,400
(Even though I know
he came with an agenda,)

27
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:05,520
(I still can't help feeling down.)

28
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,520
So…

29
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:16,880
is the plan still on?

30
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,000
Why panic?

31
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,080
Everything's under control.

32
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:27,760
Hey, Boss,

33
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,840
is it really under control?

34
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,200
Go easy on the drinks.

35
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:37,080
The doctor said
alcohol clouds your mind.

36
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:49,600
I'm perfectly clear.

37
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,880
Do I look like unclear-headed?

38
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,560
Yu Kun, haven't you done enough
to hurt her?

39
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,080
She's locking herself at home now,

40
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,990
not eating or drinking.

41
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:04,000
She even hurt herself.

42
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,280
If anything happens to her,

43
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:07,090
I'll be the first to come after you.

44
00:04:07,090 --> 00:04:09,000
Maimai, calm down. Easy.

45
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,080
Dial down the temper a bit.

46
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,050
Let's talk this through.

47
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,040
Let go!

48
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,160
Keep it up and I'll go after you too.

49
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,000
Alright.

50
00:04:17,230 --> 00:04:18,090
You...

51
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:19,680
Alright.

52
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,520
Come on, hit me.

53
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:24,900
It's not like you haven't before.

54
00:04:24,900 --> 00:04:27,400
Serves you right for doing her wrong!

55
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,200
Take good care of her for me.

56
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,520
Thank you.

57
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,040
Chen Aming.

58
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:38,360
Stop thinking so highly of yourself.

59
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,840
Ding Daang can live without you.

60
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,600
You done holding me?

61
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,560
Turns out

62
00:05:21,880 --> 00:05:24,920
violence is the most useless way
to solve anything.

63
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:36,240
Chen Aming.

64
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,520
You stole
and wore Ding Daang's dress, huh?

65
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:41,600
There's no way you could afford it.

66
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,880
Take it off.

67
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,920
Hurry up, take it off right now.

68
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,740
You're too young to be acting like this.

69
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:48,960
Trying to be a thief now?

70
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,240
Brother, say something to her.

71
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,800
I didn't steal it.

72
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,080
Move aside.

73
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,160
I said move aside!

74
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,600
Are you moving or not?

75
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,400
Not taking it off?

76
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,640
Fine, I'll help you.

77
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,520
Take it off! I said take it off now!

78
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,120
What are you doing? Let me go!

79
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:12,880
You've crossed the line, Chen Aming!

80
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:14,560
I'm warning you,

81
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:15,990
don't think I'm clueless.

82
00:06:15,990 --> 00:06:18,080
I know exactly how much rice and oil

83
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,840
your shameless mom has stolen
from my home.

84
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,480
Don't think I'm clueless.

85
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,360
A bunch of parasites.

86
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,160
Get out of my house, now.

87
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:27,940
Who are you looking for?

88
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,600
Ding Daang.

89
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,920
She's not here.

90
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,760
This is my place.

91
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,160
Don't think changing your look fools me.

92
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,320
Trying to cozy up to us,

93
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,240
aren't you?

94
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,560
It's not happening.

95
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:41,680
Ding Daang

96
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,480
is about to get engaged to President Hu.

97
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,080
Stop dreaming about things
way out of your league.

98
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,520
Leave. Now.

99
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,880
Let him in.

100
00:08:24,840 --> 00:08:25,880
What are you doing?

101
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:30,640
Ding Daang.

102
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,080
Please, stop hurting yourself.

103
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,000
If we can't change your family,

104
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,480
I'll be your shield.

105
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,160
I'll protect you for life.

106
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,080
Do me a favor

107
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:54,280
and just let me go.

108
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,360
Ding Daang.

109
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,840
You're defending him.

110
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,560
You're actually defending this jerk.

111
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,720
You're only playing with her.

112
00:10:07,160 --> 00:10:08,360
If you're serious,

113
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:10,790
I'll call off the engagement.

114
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:13,400
But right now,

115
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,320
tell her straight

116
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,120
if you'd marry her.

117
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:56,960
Hu Yitong.

118
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,200
I promise you.

119
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:05,720
The engagement goes on as planned.

120
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:15,720
Don't touch me.

121
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:20,400
An engagement gift.

122
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:23,400
Don't treat me like this.

123
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:26,960
If there's even a shred
of reluctance in you,

124
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,400
even just a flicker,

125
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:32,520
then find a way to keep me.

126
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:34,480
Alright?

127
00:11:38,280 --> 00:11:40,200
What you need more is to face reality.

128
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,240
I'm taking a gamble

129
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,840
on his last bit of sincerity.

130
00:11:46,260 --> 00:11:47,860
He might act on impulse for me once more.

131
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:49,950
You really want to marry Ding Daang?

132
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,240
I just need to reach my goal.

133
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:53,520
Anything else

134
00:11:53,520 --> 00:11:54,600
doesn't matter to me.

135
00:12:20,210 --> 00:12:27,210
♪I forgot this is a movie meant for one♪

136
00:12:31,610 --> 00:12:38,970
♪Somehow you're still here,
crying with me♪

137
00:12:43,420 --> 00:12:45,360
♪They say♪

138
00:12:45,770 --> 00:12:54,150
♪Lovers should never hold hands
while watching a sad movie♪

139
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:57,650
♪Some endings cannot be changed♪

140
00:12:57,870 --> 00:13:03,820
♪They don't belong in sweet memories♪

141
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:10,960
♪I've already lost you♪

142
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:16,440
♪Thinking of it takes my breath away♪

143
00:13:16,740 --> 00:13:22,690
♪The movie ends, so many couples around♪

144
00:13:22,690 --> 00:13:27,470
♪Yet none were ever like us♪

145
00:13:28,580 --> 00:13:32,610
♪The past will always pass♪

146
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:40,520
♪If you could still hold me tight
in your arms♪

147
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:44,240
♪I'd believe
that there are miracles in love♪

148
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:50,450
♪I'd prove
that I'm still in love with you♪

149
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:56,440
♪I've learned how to cherish
what we had♪

150
00:13:56,440 --> 00:14:02,700
♪But sadly, it's not you♪
